\c 13 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 13\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Gargaarsi Waaqayyoo Yoo Ture Iyyuu Amanachuun Hin Dhiifamu (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Hamma yoomiitti raawwattee na irraanfatta, yaa Waaqayyo? Hamma yoomiitti fuula kee na duraa dhoksita?
\m \bd 2\bd* Hamma yoomiitti lubbuun koo yaadaan dhiphatti? Hamma yoomiitti garaan koo guyyaa guutuu gadda? Hamma yoomiitti diinonni koo ana irra aanu?
\m \bd 3\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo gooftaa ko na ilaali, anaaf deebisis; hirriba du'aa akkan hin rafnetti ija koo anaaf ibsi.
\m \bd 4\bd* Diinni koo, ''Isa mo'eera'' hin jedhin, hamajaajiin koos bitintiruu kootti sonaan hin gammadin!
\m \bd 5\bd* Ani garuu gaarummaa kee amanadheera, na oolchuu keettis garaa koo guutuudhaan nan gammada.
\m \bd 6\bd* Wanta gaarii inni anaaf godheef, ani Waaqayyoon nan faarfadha.
\b 
